No worries - for the (really) quick (while you have traffic from HN) fix, stick:<p>@media only screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    .tuck-corners .headline,
    .tuck-corners h2 {
        display:none !important;
    }
}<p>at the end of your style sheet. It (should!) hide the messy bit on the homepage from smaller screens and let people see/fill in the 30 trial day form.
